    • getSchool

      public String[][] getSchool(boolean[] isProfessorPresent, Integer[] entranceStudents, int numTowers, TowerType type, Integer[] diningRoomStudents)
      Returns the completed school box with all dynamics part. The method filled the school skeleton with the dynamics part of the island
      Parameters:
      isProfessorPresent - boolean array that tell wich professor is present in the school
      entranceStudents - integer array that tell how many student for each type are present in the entrance
      numTowers - number of towers present in school
      type - type of towers present in school
      diningRoomStudents - integer array that tell how many student for each type, are present in the dining room
      Returns:
      the completed school box with all dynamics part

      coins - number of coins of the owner of te school
